[Masvingo Province is located in southeastern Zimbabwe and borders on southern Mozambique. The provinces of Zimbabwe can be seen on a map at: http://vbmap.org/pictures/africa/zimbabwe/zimbabwe-map-provinces-01.gif. - Mod.LL]

