[Mara Region is one of Tanzania's 30 administrative regions. It is located in extreme northern Tanzania, and across Lake Victoria to the northeast is southern Kenya, where cholera is also active. The region can be seen on a map at: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Tanzania_Mara_location_map.svg. - Mod.LL]

